* Disable channel authentication
ALTER QMGR CHLAUTH(DISABLED)

* Alter authinfo to make client authentication optional
ALTER AUTHINFO('DEV.AUTHINFO') AUTHTYPE(IDPWOS) CHCKCLNT(OPTIONAL) CHCKLOCL(OPTIONAL) ADOPTCTX(YES)
REFRESH SECURITY(*) TYPE(CONNAUTH)

* Alter the channel to not require authentication
ALTER CHANNEL('DEV.APP.SVRCONN') CHLTYPE(SVRCONN) MCAUSER('app') 

* Start the channel
START CHANNEL('DEV.APP.SVRCONN')
